# Wiki Discipline (applies to every session)

Shared knowledge wiki: `${WIKI_PATH}/wiki/` (`SCHEMA.md`, `index.md`, `log.md`). Full rules: `${WIKI_PATH}/CLAUDE.md`.

Shared ops journal (all tools): `${WIKI_PATH}/memory.md`.

**Capture ≠ Ingest.** Do not silently compile raw into wiki pages.

1. Before deep work: `SCHEMA.md` + `index.md` + `tail -20 ${WIKI_PATH}/memory.md`.
2. **Capture (auto):** any fetched/clipped source → `wiki/raw/` without asking. Stop there unless ingest is requested.
3. **Ingest (collaborative):** when 곽경준 says 넣어줘/소화/ingest (or after a clip when starting ingest) → read raw → present 3–5 takeaways in Korean → ask what to emphasize → only then write wiki pages + index/log. One source at a time unless he says 알아서/배치. If you fetched during other work: save to raw and ask “ingest 할까?” — do not full-ingest unprompted.
4. Substantial **query** answers (comparisons/analyses/connections) → still auto-file to `queries/` or `comparisons/` + index/log. Skip one-off fact checks.
5. `wiki/raw/` is immutable. Contradictions → `> ⚠️ 상충:`, never silent overwrite.
6. Pine/code analysis: capture to `wiki/raw/` → discuss takeaways → then analysis page + registry gap in 📌.
7. Session decisions → same `${WIKI_PATH}/memory.md`. Taste → `owner-taste.md`. Ideas → `ideas-inbox.md`. Answer 곽경준 in Korean.
